          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The Company Man",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a grim capitalist satire wrapped in a 2D action-platformer. With clear inspirations from the likes of the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Mega Man ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "franchise and produced by writers for ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The Onion",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " and apparently, that is exactly what I want from a game. Play as an entry-level employee fighting your way up the corporate ladder… literally. As Jim, mild-mannered and familiarly-named pencil pusher, you must traverse sprawling “departments”, complete with challenging platforming, innumerable background jokes and a vast assortment of enemies to dispatch.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQcP1qMg4EI",
        "html": "<iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQcP1qMg4EI?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>",
        "metadata": {
          "title": "The Company Man - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch",
          "author_name": "Nintendo",
          "author_url": "https://www.youtube.com/c/nintendo",
          "height": 113,
